content: are all these updated or are these all the most important topics to know?
replyContent: We make an effort to make sure this is these questions stay up to date, and to the best of our knowledge all questions are current. The topics covered are the ones we have determined are most frequently asked at Army Boards. Please note this app focuses on the most frequently asked questions, but its possible other questions may arise at the board.

content: Not worth the money. There are a lot of subjects that are not covered and of those that were there are not enough questions. Plus I noticed some inaccurate and very basic answers. I bought this app in hopes that I would not have to kill trees to print flashcards but it was not a very useful tool. Only benefit was I could study anywhere without using my data to access the internet.
